    let steakText = ["What does Everest Steak mean? Simply, that with our passion for quality and impeccable attention to detail, we want to ensure that your steak is hand cut, prepared and broiled precisely to your liking.\nWe've elevated the steak dinner to an art, and we believe you'll savor your meal as much as we enjoy serving them.\nEverest Steak is one of the special steak offered by Everest Burger at Lukla. Everest Burger the good varieties of Steak and many choices of hard and soft drinks. Everest Steak is  mostly demanded by our visitors.\nAt Everest Burger, you can enjoy an delicious steak or any Everest Special food.", "Everest Burger is renowned for its ethereal steaks, made from a proprietary blend of organic, super-prime beef .  All of the steaks prepared by our experienced Chef with sea salt, black pepper and fresh rosemary to achieve otherworldly tenderness and flavor.", "At Everest Burger you will also adore our fresh chicken and other menu items every bit as much.\nYou’ll find us in the perfect location for travelers, with many local hotels and the airport being close by. This makes us a popular stop for visitors away from home. Nothing will make your trip or vacation more enjoyable than a great hand-cut chicken steak, delicious smothered or roasted chicken or Everest special steak. You’ll also love our dessert menu!\n\nSo many restaurants change over the years because chefs come and go. We’re happy to tell you that with our family-owned and operated restaurant, we have had the same chef since we opened. You’ll taste the difference that our experience provides! Whether you come see us at Everest Burger for breakfast, lunch, or dinner, you won’t be disappointed!"]
    
